Special thanks to Clifford Heath for his help putting together the radio demo, and the folks at the Victorian ARDF group for connecting us.

videos.title: The Real Story of Oppenheimer
videos.description:
J. Robert Oppenheimer forever changed the course of history. He may be the most important physicist to have ever lived. Part of this video is sponsored by Wren. Offset your carbon footprint on Wren: ‚Äãhttps://www.wren.co/start/veritasium1 For the first 100 people who sign up, I will personally pay for the first month of your subscription!

If you want to learn more about Oppenheimer, I strongly recommend the book ‚ÄúAmerican Prometheus‚Äù By Kai Bird and Martin Sherwin. It was the inspiration for Christopher Nolan's 2023 film "Oppenheimer", which won multiple awards, including Oscars in 2024 for Best Picture and Best Actor (Cillian Murphy).

videos.title: Bubble Bass' Order (Wendy's Krabby Patty Challenge)
videos.description:
Bubble Bass' Order. The Myth. The Enigma.

This challenge has been on my radar for YEARS! So, with the Krabby Patty Kollab meal just dropping and Wendy's, I could finally have the chance to build Bubble Bass' Order with "actual" Krabby Patties.

My Breakdown is as follows...

Double Triple = 2 Patties, 3 Cheese
Bossy Deluxe: = Lettuce, Pickles, Onions, Tomatoes (Bossy = Both top and Bottom)
On a Raft = Toast instead of Buns

4x4 = 4 Patties, 4 Cheese
Animal Style = In-n-Out Animal Fries on top
Extra Shingles = Extra Pickles
With a Shimmy = Grape Jelly
And a Squeeze = Orange Juice (on the side)
Light Axle Grease = Light Butter
Make it Cry = Extra Onions
Burn It = BURN IT
Let it swim = Extra Krabby Patty 'Secret Sause' 

Reddit Breakdown - https://www.reddit.com/r/spongebob/comments/3t5qzm/comment/cx3b7he/?utm_source=share&utm_medium=web2x&context=3
Binging with Babish's Video - https://youtu.be/Y8hi6A5MPVY

Jump Boost when holding the Crossbow (Repeating & Always Active):
execute as @a[nbt={SelectedItem:{id:"minecraft:crossbow",Count:1b}}] run effect give @s minecraft:jump_boost 1 18 true

Sonic Boom effect on Fireworks (Repeating & Always Active):
execute as @e[type=minecraft:firework_rocket] at @s run particle minecraft:sonic_boom ~ ~ ~ 0.1 0.1 0.1 0 10

Gives fire particles on the Fireworks (Repeating & Always Active):
execute as @e[type=minecraft:firework_rocket,nbt={Life:25}] at @s run particle minecraft:flame ~ ~ ~ 0.5 0.5 0.5 0.3 10000 force

(Attached to the Fire Particles Command Block) Makes the Fireworks explode (Chain & Always Active):
execute as @e[type=minecraft:firework_rocket,nbt={Life:25}] at @s run summon minecraft:creeper ~ ~ ~ {ExplosionRadius:10b,Fuse:0}

videos.title: Addressing My Mental Health.. Selling My House and Getting Help
videos.description:
There has been so many major life changes for me this year and I'm ready to share them all with you.
It's time to address my mental health and be very transparent. I've had so many silent personal struggles, public feuds and ALOT of mental trauma. Caused by ME, my past actions and people from my past. I've had TOO MUCH loss and have been slowly healing.

It's time to also say goodbye to California for awhile.. I'm selling my giant house in LA, I've donated and sold all my clothes and I'm starting the next chapter of my life. Please listen with an open heart and mind. Thank you to everyone who has stood by me through all the success AND the ugly. I love you so much. If you are struggling with mental health issues or depression, NEVER feel ashamed to ask for help. I waited too long and I'm grateful every day for making the choice to heal.

videos.title: Off Road Racing With Big Toys!
videos.description:
Thank you so much for watching today. Join us at this upcoming event :) 

The inaugural Glassrock Offroad Fest will be held November 3-4, in Glassrock, Ohio.

Activities during the event will include pit bike racing, a truck/jeep/SxS/Offroad show where you can show off your ride and check out other offroad vehicles, sand drag racing and of course trail riding on nearly 260 acres. If you need a break from the activities there will be bounce houses, axe throwing, bow and arrow shooting, fishing, and multiple food trucks to choose from.   More activities are added daily to make this the fall offroad festival you don‚Äôt want to miss.

Admission to GOF is only $20 per person 13 yrs or older.  12 and under is free.  Because this is the inaugural year parking and camping will be free. Gates open at 5pm Friday Nov 3 and we gotta kick you out by Noon on Sunday Nov 5!

"Wreck This Christmas 2" - Introducing a heartwarming holiday tale about two sisters at Christmas. Follow Tia, a sweet girl who loves all things Christmas, as she spreads cheer and bakes cookies for Santa with her elves.
